                    "body": "We could pretty easily add a \"total length\" field to the file footer, though, which would be more convenient https://github.com/apache/arrow/blob/master/format/File.fbs#L33",
                    "updateAuthor": {
                        "self": "https://issues.apache.org/jira/rest/api/2/user?username=wesm",
                        "name": "wesm",
                        "key": "wesmckinn",
                        "avatarUrls": {
